13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 63 O.S. 2021, Section 1-242.4, as
15 amended by Section 1, Chapter 263, O.S.L. 2024 (63 O.S. Supp. 2024,
16 Section 1-242.4), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1-242.4. A. The Maternal Mortality Review Committee
18 shall be composed of eleven (11) members, or their designees, as
19 follows:
20 1. Eight of the members shall be:
21 a. the Chair of the Oklahoma Chapter of the American
22 College of Obstetricians and Gynecologists,
23 b. the President of the Oklahoma Chapter of the American
24 College of Nurse-Midwives,
